{"tid":1309020,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"政治數學題 請問香港有幾多香港人","createTime":"2019-07-12T04:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T01:42:23.000Z","uid":173326,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6f4afdbaf4a73214dfde42d7603123f459d803d8","tid":1309020,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:57:16.000Z","msg":"根據保安局在回覆毛孟靜問題時呈交的數字，由 1997 年 7 月至 2018年底，以單程證來港人士累計達 103.3 萬人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Single20CARD_dmsW2_1200x0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FSingle20CARD_dmsW2_1200x0.JPG&h=f909dd16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n引用自立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E6%94%B9%E5%96%AE%E7%A8%8B%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%9A%B4%E6%A0%BC%E5%AF%A9%E6%A0%B8-%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%94%A8%E7%9B%A1-150-%E9%85%8D%E9%A1%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2594%25B3%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2596%25AE%25E7%25A8%258B%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25BA%25A6-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259A%25B4%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%25A0%25B8-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%259A%25E7%2594%25A8%25E7%259B%25A1-150-%25E9%2585%258D%25E9%25A1%258D%2F&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=c0fc972a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2594%25B3%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2596%25AE%25E7%25A8%258B%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25BA%25A6-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259A%25B4%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%25A0%25B8-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%259A%25E7%2594%25A8%25E7%259B%25A1-150-%25E9%2585%258D%25E9%25A1%258D%2F&h=5521163e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E6%94%B9%E5%96%AE%E7%A8%8B%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%9A%B4%E6%A0%BC%E5%AF%A9%E6%A0%B8-%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%94%A8%E7%9B%A1-150-%E9%85%8D%E9%A1%8D/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">103萬人來港，佢地會講住蝗語去組織新嘅蝗語家庭，而且係攞永久身份證。<br />\n<br />\n請問去到今日，香港仲有幾多家庭係講廣東話？</span></span>"},{"pid":"39f3a3721960da08ecf9601a14d6f33c5eafd156","tid":1309020,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:32:01.000Z","msg":"過多十年，個答案係0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a9b5662a450ed8b85b078d23d4bbc98199dd0f","tid":1309020,"uid":138331,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"嗰103萬中嘅後生隨時衝得仲前過你，搞乜分化。宜家係要停止太多人來，而唔係話來咗嘅唔係香港人。"},{"pid":"fa828d3d930715c7dc2513f5fee5b8ad1a9d5499","tid":1309020,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70a9b5662a450ed8b85b078d23d4bbc98199dd0f","tid":1309020,"uid":138331,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"嗰103萬中嘅後生隨時衝得仲前過你，搞乜分化。宜家係要停止太多人來，而唔係話來咗嘅唔係香港人。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:20:53.000Z","msg":"我講緊個班嚟入侵香港嘅大陸人，而唔係嚟學習香港文化嘅人。前者可能會學習做個香港人、會支持民主，但後者只會賣港。<br />\n當然150可能兩者都有，但實在太冒險，而家香港要抗爭嘅人唔少，冇必要任由150俾機會大陸人滲透。<br />\n嚟入侵個自己唔學廣東話就算，仲當眾用普通話大聲講野，根本唔尊重香港本身嘅文化，我諗呢啲唔叫香港人。<br />\n中、港就係要分得清清楚楚，否則只會係一國一制。"},{"pid":"fbeba8bb34b5143a43e358ee52ac1138bdd4f0ca","tid":1309020,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T01:39:47.000Z","msg":"唔知<br />\n我淨係知1997到2018香港人口數目咁啱又係100萬左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10aa7df947c7acbf493c51e3689dc6405a604251","tid":1309020,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbeba8bb34b5143a43e358ee52ac1138bdd4f0ca","tid":1309020,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T01:39:47.000Z","msg":"唔知<br />\n我淨係知1997到2018香港人口數目咁啱又係100萬左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T01:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}